Output demo/etf.gif

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "cd ~/Projects/me/entire-fzf"
Enter
Show

Sleep 500ms
Type "etf"
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Navigate and select a session in fzf
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Navigate and select an action
Down
Down
Enter
Sleep 3s
